Class RDF

java.lang.Object
org.apache.jena.vocabulary.RDF
public class RDF extends Object
Vocabulary definition for the standard RDF. See RDF schema (turtle).

    • PlainLiteral

      public static final Resource PlainLiteral
      This property is used explicitly in facet restrictions. Also, it can be used as a literal type (e.g., 'test'^^rdf:PlainLiteral) in old ontologies based on RDF-1.0
      See Also:
      • rdf:PlainLiteral: A Datatype for RDF Plain Literals (Second Edition)

    • langRange

      public static final Property langRange
      This property is used in facet restrictions. The facet rdf:langRange can be used to refer to a subset of strings containing the language tag.
      See Also:
      • rdf:langRange
